---
// Sekcja Rozwiązanie - dopiero teraz oferta
---

<section id="dla-placowek" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Jak możemy pomóc
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Karta 1: Szkolenia -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-dark rounded-2xl p-8 text-white hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">
          Szkolenia
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Praktyczne warsztaty i kursy dla położnych prowadzące przez doświadczonych praktyków medycznych.
        </p>
        <a href="/szkolenia" class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          Zobacz ofertę
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Karta 2: Projekty rozwojowe -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-accent-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-white hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">
          Projekty rozwojowe
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Długoterminowe programy wsparcia: Położna na swoim, grupy Mastermind i społeczności eksperckie.
        </p>
        <a href="/projekty" class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold hover:text-primary transition-colors">
          Poznaj projekty
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Karta 3: Rekrutacja dla placówek -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-700 to-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">
          Rekrutacja dla placówek
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Kompleksowa pomoc w rekrutacji specjalistów medycznych dla klinik, gabinetów i szpitali.
        </p>
        <a href="/dla-placowek/rekrutacja" class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          Zapytaj o rekrutację
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
